  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1067">
<l>irappa ṉirappārai yellā mirappiṟ</l>
<l>karappā riravaṉmi ṉeṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I beseech all beggars and say, "If you need to beg, never beg of those who give unwillingly."</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
